;Tuesday, 10 February
:Spot fires from Kinglake complex fires merged to form the ''Maroondah/Yarra complex''.

;Tuesday, 17 February
:Six fires still burnt out of control, with another nineteen contained.<ref name="Healesville">{{Cite news| title =Winds cause nervous moments for Healesville | publisher = The Age | work= Fairfax Media | date = 17 February 2009 | url = http://www.theage.com.au/national/winds-cause-nervous-moments-for-healesville-20090217-89gu.html | accessdate =17 February 2009 | location=Melbourne}}</ref>
