**[[Chile]] (1)<ref>{{Cite news| title = Chilena muere en incendios de Australia | url = http://www.chilesomostodos.gov.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=527&Itemid=7 | accessdate = 21 February 2009 }}</ref>
